---
import Layout from "@/components/base/Layout.astro";
import PhotoFrame from "@/components/ui/PhotoFrame.astro";
import { BUSINESS } from "@/utils/constants";
---

<Layout seo={{ title: `About ${BUSINESS.practitioner}, ${BUSINESS.credentials}` }}>
  <section class="pt-28 pb-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="section-label mb-4">About Your Practitioner</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">
          {BUSINESS.practitioner}, {BUSINESS.credentials}
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-charcoal/60 max-w-2xl">
          {BUSINESS.credentialsFull} — {BUSINESS.location}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio + Photo -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <!-- Photo Column -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <PhotoFrame
            alt={`${BUSINESS.practitioner}, ${BUSINESS.credentials}`}
            aspectRatio="4/5"
            class="shadow-lg sticky top-24"
          />

          <!-- Credentials list -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              { label: "Board Certified (BCSI)", desc: "IASI Board Certification — the field's highest credential" },
              { label: "500+ Hours Training", desc: "IASI-recognized program at the Structura Institute" },
              { label: "Fully Insured", desc: "Professional liability coverage for your peace of mind" },
              { label: "Evidence-Based", desc: "Protocols grounded in modern fascial research" },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-[16px] bg-brand-paper border border-brand-teal/5 p-4">
                <div class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-[12px] bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-brand-teal border border-brand-teal/10">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal">{item.label}</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-brand-charcoal/50">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio Column -->
        <div class="prose-cosmic space-y-6">
          <p>
            Have you ever noticed how your body seems to remember your day long after you've
            clocked out? Maybe it's the way your shoulders creep up toward your ears during
            a long afternoon at your desk, or that subtle "locked up" feeling in your back
            that's started to feel like a normal part of life. I'm {BUSINESS.practitioner}, and I believe
            your body has an incredible story to tell — and sometimes, it just needs a little
            help finding a more comfortable narrative.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-10 mb-4">Why Structural Integration</h2>
          <p>
            I came to Structural Integration because I was tired of watching the people I
            care about feel physically "dismantled" by our modern, sedentary world. Think of
            your body's fascia — the connective tissue that wraps everything inside you — like
            a wetsuit that's become a bit too tight or twisted. It shapes how you move,
            breathe, and even how you feel in your own skin.
          </p>
          <p>
            The BCSI credential — earned through 500+ hours of specialized training and a
            rigorous IASI board exam — represents the field's highest professional designation.
            As a Board Certified Structural Integrator, I don't just "fix" problems; I work
            with you to unwind those old patterns and find a sense of ease that you might have
            forgotten was possible.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-teal mt-10 mb-4">My Approach</h2>
          <p>
            Take a moment right now to just notice your breath. Where does it go? Does it
            feel like it has room to expand, or does it feel compressed? My work at Cosmic
            Calibrations is about creating that room — giving your structure the space and
            length it needs to thrive.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every session is a collaboration. I listen to what your body is communicating
            through its holding patterns, asymmetries, and restrictions. Then we work together —
            through precise manual techniques and your own movement awareness — to release
            what's been stuck and integrate what's been disconnected.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm honored to be part of the Calibration Collective here in Austin, and I'd love
            to help you rediscover what it feels like to live in a body that feels balanced
            and grounded.
          </p>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-brand-teal/10">
            <a
              href="/#contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-brand-teal text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 text-base hover:bg-brand-teal-light shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all"
            >
              Book a Free 15-Min Consult
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round">
                <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
